    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle presents in solid good condition and represents a reliable, well-maintained used car. The exterior shows the expected minor wear for its age \u2014 a few small scratches and light surface scuffs here and there \u2014 but no significant dents, rust, or structural damage. The paint retains good overall luster. The interior is clean and functional, with normal seat wear and no major tears or damage to the upholstery. All primary features and controls operate as intended. Mechanically, the car runs well \u2014 the engine starts reliably, transmission shifts smoothly, and brakes are responsive. It has been regularly serviced and is ready for daily driving without any immediate major repairs anticipated. A solid, honest choice for a buyer looking for dependable transportation at a fair price.",
